markdownRemark.html: I'm a Robotic Fabrication Expert. I am currently running the MSD Robotics Lab at the University of Melbourne. My areas of interest include plastic and clay 3D printing, reinforcement learning, and mobile fabrication robotics. You can view my publications, my code or my work. Please feel free to contact me contact me.
markdownRemark.rawMarkdownBody: I'm a Robotic Fabrication Expert. I am currently running the [MSD Robotics Lab](https://msd.unimelb.edu.au/maker-spaces/robotics-lab) at the University of Melbourne. My areas of interest include **plastic and clay 3D printing**, **reinforcement learning**, and **mobile fabrication robotics**. You can view my **publications**, my [code](https://github.com/ryanpennings/) or my **work**. Please feel free to contact me **contact me**.
